OL,3,CPolice face probe over woman left in
OL,4,Cvegetative state by abusive family
OL,6,FThe police watchdog will investigate
OL,7,Fwhether there were missed
OL,8,Fopportunities to protect a vulnerable
OL,9,Fwoman from the relatives who left her
OL,10,Fin a vegetative state.
OL,12,FAmbreen Sheikh was 30 when she
OL,13,Fsuffered a catastrophic brain injury
OL,14,Fafter being given an anti-diabetes
OL,15,Fdrug she did not need in 2015.
OL,17,FFamily members waited two or three
OL,18,Fdays before calling an ambulance after
OL,19,Fshe collapsed at her home in
OL,20,FHuddersfield.
