OL,6,FMedics found Mrs Sheikh, who had been
OL,7,Fbrought from Pakistan to the UK for an
OL,8,Farranged marriage, had also been
OL,9,Fdoused in a caustic substance.
OL,11,FHer husband, 31-year-old Asgar Sheikh,
OL,12,Fwas among last week.
OL,14,FSheikh, along with his father Khalid,
OL,15,F55, mother Shabnam, 52, and sister
OL,16,FShagufa, 29, were in December.
