OL,4,Cvegetative state by abusive family
OL,6,FAsgar Sheikh, Shabnam Sheikh and
OL,7,FShagufa Sheikh and another sibling,
OL,8,FSakalyne Sheikh, were also found
OL,9,Fguilty of perverting the course of
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,FThe court heard officers attended the
OL,13,Ffamily property in Clara Street on 12
OL,14,FJuly 2015 following a report of
OL,15,Fconcern for Mrs Sheikh's welfare `
OL,16,Falmost three weeks before she was
OL,17,Fadmitted to Calderdale Royal Hospital
OL,18,Fwith severe chemical burns and a brain
OL,19,Finjury.
