OL,6,FMrs Sheikh remains in a vegetative
OL,7,Fstate with no prospect of recovery
OL,8,Falmost nine years later.
OL,10,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,11,FConduct has launched an investigation
OL,12,Finto the contact officers had with the
OL,13,Ffamily and the "actions and decision-
OL,14,Fmaking" of those involved.
OL,16,FIOPC regional director Emily Barry
OL,17,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with Ms Sheikh
OL,18,Fand her loved ones, as well as all
OL,19,Fthose affected by this deeply
OL,20,Fdistressing incident.
