OL,6,F"In light of the comments made during
OL,7,Fthe recent court hearing, and the
OL,8,Funimaginable suffering she has
OL,9,Fendured, it is only right that a
OL,10,Fthorough investigation takes place to
OL,11,Funderstand the nature and extent of
OL,12,Fthe police interaction with Ms Sheikh
OL,13,Fin July 2015.
OL,15,F"This will be carried out entirely
OL,16,Findependently of the police and
OL,17,Fconsider whether there were any missed
OL,18,Fopportunities to safeguard her in the
OL,19,Fdays and weeks before she was admitted
OL,20,Fto hospital."
